<ab facs="#facs_150_r2l27">Joſt von Merhern den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> cʒu Prünne <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat / <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
