</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_150" id="74v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Der grossen stat czu Prag </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        weisheit nehst <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> von <expan>sölch<ex>er</ex></expan> habe
                            <add>und <expan>kauffma<ex>n</ex>s<ex>chaft</ex></expan></add>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, als vor <expan>czeite<ex>n</ex></expan> der
                                <expan>hochg<ex>eporn</ex></expan> fürst und
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>
<expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan> Jost von Merhern den
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> czu Prünne
                            <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> hat, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> uns
                        die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> wol <add>zu wissen getan</add>, wie sich
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> darynne vast gemüet hab und in gar
                        fürderlich und <expan>beholffe<ex>n</ex></expan> gen
                                <expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>margr<ex>af</ex></expan> Josten <expan>gewese<ex>n</ex></expan> sey,
                        des wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersame<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>euntschaft</ex></expan> mit <expan>gancze<ex>m</ex></expan>
                        fleisz <expan>danke<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>,
                        daz ir fürbaz den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> ewr günstig hilff und
                                <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> darynne
                            <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> gütlich beweisen wöllet. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> wir umb <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan>
<expan>ers<ex>amkeit</ex></expan>
<expan>allcz<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
